- Build a simple facial recognition model
- Given an image, tell us whether it contains a face or not
- Obtain and format data
    - Resizing and reshaping
    - Assign labels
    - Shuffle data and separate into training and testing
- Build the model in pycharm
    - Use keras to build a conv neural network
    - Train and test the model
    - Save the model to pb file
- Build android app
    - Import the model and set up project
    - Build UI
    - Format image data
    - Process data and display results